    "description": "RACCOON HOLDINGS, Inc. creates and provides infrastructure BtoB transactions in Japan. The company operates SUPER DELIVERY, a wholesale purchasing site for manufacturers of apparel and general good, and businesses, such as retail stores, restaurants, and hair salons; COREC, a cloud-based ordering system; and SD Export for developing overseas market. It offers Paid, a BtoB payment service; online receivables guarantee services; and guaranteed online services for small and medium-sized business, as well as rent guarantee services for individuals and business use for offices or stores. In addition, the company offers URIHO, sales guarantee service that guarantees the price of transactions in place of the accounts even if the account does not pay due to financial difficulties or bankruptcy. The company was formerly known as Raccoon Co., Ltd. and changed its name to RACCOON HOLDINGS, Inc. in November 2018. RACCOON HOLDINGS, Inc. was founded in 1993 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
